quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  60,1,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe Alla gollir…ìe ko O sariyani…ìe, wotee nanngire a√±…ìe Alla e any…ìe mon heed…ìe e sehilaa…ìe …ìe nji…óandirton, yeddu…ìe ko ardi e mon ummaade e nelaa…óo e diine, yaltinoo…ìe nelaa…óo e galle makko, …ìe njaltina on e galleeji mon ka Makka, …ìe ngaynatah jiidigal wonah en…óam, …ìe mba…óiri …óum tan ko ngoon…óin…óon ko Alla joom mon, wotee golle …óuum si tawii taki mon yaltude ko jihaadi laawol Alla e yiilaade weluya Alla, ho…óon ndeeya…ìe kabaruuji juul…ìe ngam yidde …ìe, Mina anndi ko mbirnaton e ko pe√±√±inton, hay ndiga wirnataako Mi, kala keednu…óo wolla yi…ói heefer…ìe o accii laawol pooccingol, o majjii goongo o deestiima peewal."
  60,2,"Si…ìe peewnatiima e mon …ìe kollira ko…ìe cuu…óatno e nga√±ngu, …ìe lorlira mon juu…óe ma…ì…ìe piggal, …ìe mbellita …óem…óe ma…ì…ìe ∆¥attooje e yennude, …ìe ngoo…óe de njeddaton Alla e nelaa…óo makko ngonon yeru mum en."
  60,3,"Nafatah mon jiidigal mon, wonah …ìi…ì…ìe mon si on keednii heefer…ìe ngam mum en, √±ande darnga Alla seernda mon, yim…ìe aljanna naata aljanna yim…ìe yiite naata yiite, alah nafoowo go…ó…óo o, Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko, hay ndiga wirnataako mbo e golle mon, ma o yo…ì mon …óe."
  60,4,"Woodaniina mon-onon goon…óin…ìe- √±eemtinirgal mo∆¥∆¥al e Ibraahiima-yo o his- e gonn…óin…ìe wondunoo…ìe e makko, nde …ìe yim…ìe mum heeferee…ìe : komin his…ìe mon e ko ndewaton e sanamuuji ko wonah Alla, min njeddii ko ngon…óon ko e diine, fee√±i hakkunde men ga√±ndiral haa ngoon…óinon Alla gooto O, wotee ndenndinee Mbo e hay gooto, on potno hisnaade e yim…ìe mon heeferee…ìe hono mon, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima-yo o his- ngol o wiino baabiiko, ma mi yaafnano ma Alla, wote √±eemtinee mbo e …óuum, sabu …óum wonno ko adii nde Ibraahiima fi…ìtato e baaba makko, alanah juul…óo nde o yaafnanato cirku…óo, mi du√±antaama e lepte Alla he hay huunde, joomi amen ko e Ma min tuugnoto, ko e Ma min nduttoto tuub…ìe, ko e Ma woni ruttorde √±ande darnga."
  60,5,"joomi amen wota A wa…ó min fitina wonande …ìeen heeferee…ìe hono nde nguurtataa…ìe e dow amen …ìe mbi*a: si …ìe wonna e goonga Alla wuurtataana amen e dow ma…ì…ìe, habran amen bakkatuuji amen, ko Aan woni pooloowo mbo fooletaake, √±ee√±…óu…óo e tagu makko e sariya makko e hoddira makko."